the Ingredients needed to make a red Velvet Cake are:
 1. Flour
 2. Baking Soda
 3. Butter
 4. Eggs
 5. Vinilla Essence
 6. Red Velvet Food Colouring


Step 1

Mix the butter and sugar 

step 2

Put in the eggs. one at a time.Mix to smooth paste.

step 3

seperately seive the flour and Baking powder.

Step 4

mix the Dry Ingredients with the wet Ingredients
Add Vinilla essence andred Velvet food Couloring.

Step 5
Pour into Baking Dish and Bake at 170 degrees C for 1 hour





